						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of 90 sheep for a perpetual lamp in the same temple, left with two shepherds of the village, by a certain <hi rend="bold">Māṟaṉ Malaipe••• .</hi> the headman of Puliyūr in Ārumpuliyūr of Aruvāḻa-nāḍu.</p>						

						</summary>
